description.narrative: As a contribution to quality in primary education, UNICEF supported the Ministry of Education in completing the curricular materials for grades 5 and 6. Curricular materials for Grade 5 were finalized, including manuals for students and guides for teachers. Curriculum for grade 6 is under development. For grade 1 to 4, illustrations of teachers' guides and textbooks are being finalized. They will be tested in 2020 on a pilot basis with financial support from the World Bank and the Global Partnership for Education. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/01/2018
